@{B}Project@{UB}

 Hide

 Quit

 About

I don't have to describe these, do I?


@{B}Misc@{UB}

Save current list

saves the currently displayed information in the listview to the file selected
in the asl file requester which will pop up.


@{B}Settings@{UB}

en-disable columns

with  the  items  in  this  submenu  you  can  disable  or enable the columns
displayed in the listview.


snapshot window

stores the current window size and position in the appropriate tooltypes.


sort panel

makes the 'Sort Panel' visible or invisible.


